{
  "stem": "16792.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 348.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- before we do our, our job, before we do something, we know-- not 100%, because a lot of the time I lost a lot of people, too.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we know about 90%.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We know what we're doing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we catch, we don't, we don't-- when we go in to the German side already [INAUDIBLE], is a group of people which goes in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The group of people are professionals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's four people, four people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They are professional in Judo, in karate, in knife throwing, in clubs, everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they have only a gun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They don't have machine guns.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We have machine guns, all of them around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then this four people doing the job-- now this is the four they're calling it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is the people which catching people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's all what they're doing, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is people which is cut out, a left cut and a right cut.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The left cut and right cut is normally between five and six people each side, which they do nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Only they protect this four people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They don't let in anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If something happened, they fight him away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "After that, we have [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is a group which is behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we cover up all of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And this is-- whenever I go for a big job-- I did, I don't go anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But whenever I did go to a big job, I made a sketch how to do it and which way to do it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I'm the person which is in charge, nobody else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't care it's a general.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He must listen to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Or he's a major.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It's not important.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I am the top man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And this is the way I make the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And normally, we have a, a group, 140 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
